commentary: Abu Jayed to Balbirnie, OUT end of a promising innings. And what a terrible way to go. Looks to take on the short ball but this doesn't come on and he's through with the stroke, cramped for room. Did he get a little globve on the way through to Mushfiqur? No conclusive proof. Given out so he has to go. Oh, there's no review. How unfortunate? Richard Kettleborough the umpire in question.
